            "AWS" => "Please hire me, so I can keep footing the AWS bill. ğŸ’¸",
            "AWS_Docker" => "Please hire me, so I can keep footing the AWS bill and run them Dockers. ğŸ’¸",
            _ => "Please hire me, so I can keep feeding my cat. ğŸ’¸"
        };
    }
}
